<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Interview Confirmation</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Interview Confirmation</h2>
    <p>Dear <strong><%= employerName %></strong>,</p>
    <p>
      We are pleased to inform you that an interview has been scheduled regarding the application for the job role <strong><%= jobTitle %></strong>.
    </p>
    <p>Please find the details below:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Interview Date:</strong> <%= interviewDate %></li>
      <li><strong>Interview Time:</strong> <%= interviewTime %></li>
      <li><strong>Location/Mode:</strong> <%= interviewLocation %></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Thank you, and we look forward to your participation.</p>
    <br />
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p><strong>Job Portal Team</strong></p>
  </body>
</html>
